    • solve

      public static TSPTW.TSPTWSolution solve(TSPTW.TSPTWInstance instance)
      TODO given an instance TSPTW.TSPTWInstance to solve (a number of nodes, distance between them and their time windows TSPTW.TimeWindow), give the order of visit of each nodes minimizing the traveled distance of the vehicle use TSPTW.TSPTWInstance.distances or TSPTW.TSPTWInstance.distance(int, int) to compute distances the vehicle can arrive at a node n before the beginning of its time window TSPTW.TimeWindow.getEarliest() if this is the case, the departure occurs at the beginning of its time window the depot is always located at node 0 DEPOT and has the longest time window
      Parameters:
      instance - instance to solve
      Returns:
      valid solution minimizing the traveled distance of the vehicle
